msgid "Invalid file type. Only JPG, PNG, and PDF are accepted."
msgstr "نوع الملف غير صالح. يُقبل فقط JPG وPNG وPDF."

#. translators: %s: Date and time when the receipt was uploaded (e.g. 2025-01-17 14:30:00).
